<p>rails项目中 <code class="highlighter-rouge">Gemfile</code>文件设置笔记:</p>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> <span class="n">gem</span> <span class="s1">'pg'</span>
 <span class="n">gem</span> <span class="s1">'rails_12factor'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="ss">group: :production</span>

 <span class="n">group</span> <span class="ss">:development</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="ss">:test</span> <span class="k">do</span>
   <span class="n">gem</span> <span class="s1">'sqlite3'</span>
   <span class="c1"># ....</span>
 <span class="k">end</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">database.yml</code>:</p>

